trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Ger stöd för designtid i en visuell designer för den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control is used as a container for other controls, especially when controls are generated programmatically.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontrollen används som en behållare för andra kontroller, särskilt när kontroller genereras programmässigt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>

trans-unit.source: The PanelDesigner class provides design-time support for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> controls in a visual designer.
trans-unit.target: Klassen PanelDesigner söder designläge <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontroller i en visuell designer.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>

trans-unit.source: However, for all new implementations of the Panel control, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner> instead of the PanelDesigner.
trans-unit.target: Men för alla nya implementeringar av panelen kontrollen använder den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner>i stället för PanelDesigner.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner>

trans-unit.source: In a visual designer, when you switch from Source to Design view, the markup source code that describes the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control is parsed and a design-time version of the control is created on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: I en visuell designer när du växlar från källan till designvyn markeringen källkod som beskriver den associerade <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontroll analyseras och en designläge version av kontrollen har skapats i designvyn.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>

trans-unit.source: When you switch back to Source view, the design-time control is persisted to markup source code and edited into the markup for the Web page.
trans-unit.target: När du växlar tillbaka till vyn källa beständig markering källkoden designläge kontrollen och redigeras i koden för webbsidan.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A> method maps a specified property and value to a specified markup style.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A>metoden mappar en angiven egenskap och värdet till en angiven markup style.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.OnBehaviorAttached%2A> method provides notification when a behavior is attached to the designer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.OnBehaviorAttached%2A>metoden ger meddelanden när ett beteende som är kopplat till designern.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.OnBehaviorAttached%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner> class when it creates the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control or a copy of that control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework internt skapar en ny instans av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner>klassen när det skapas den associerade <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontroll eller en kopia av kontrollen i designvyn.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Maps a specified property and value to a specified markup style.
trans-unit.target: Mappar en angiven egenskap och värdet till ett angivet markup-format.

trans-unit.source: The MapPropertyToStyle method provides special handling for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.BackImageUrl%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.HorizontalAlign%2A> properties, but calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ReadWriteControlDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A> base method for all other values of the `propName` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Metoden MapPropertyToStyle innehåller särskild hantering för den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.BackImageUrl%2A>och <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.HorizontalAlign%2A>Egenskaper, men anrop i <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ReadWriteControlDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A>bas-metoden för alla andra värden för den `propName` parameter.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ReadWriteControlDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.HorizontalAlign%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.BackImageUrl%2A>

trans-unit.source: A string containing the property name.
trans-unit.target: En sträng som innehåller egenskapens namn.

trans-unit.source: An object that is the property value.
trans-unit.target: Ett objekt som är egenskapens värde.

trans-unit.source: Provides notification when a behavior is attached to the designer.
trans-unit.target: Ger meddelanden när ett beteende som är kopplad till designern.

trans-unit.source: The OnBehaviorAttached method calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ReadWriteControlDesigner.OnBehaviorAttached%2A> base method.

Then the OnBehaviorAttached maps the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.BackImageUrl%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.HorizontalAlign%2A> properties to the appropriate style by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A> method, if these properties are defined.
trans-unit.target: OnBehaviorAttached mappar den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.BackImageUrl%2A>och <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.HorizontalAlign%2A>egenskaper till lämpligt format med hjälp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A>metoden, om dessa egenskaper har definierats.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelDesigner.MapPropertyToStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.HorizontalAlign%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.BackImageUrl%2A>
